↓

Create Monitoring Capability

↓

AI recommends Information Sources

↓

AI creates Connector Definition

↓

User approves

↓

Connector Instance

↓

Runtime

↓

Raw Records

↓

AI Interpretation

↓

Mapping Suggestions

↓

Knowledge Objects

↓

Risk Intelligence

↓

Dashboard

↓

Recommendations

---

# Demo Scenario

1. Select enterprise risk categories.
2. Select risk factors to monitor.
3. AI recommends suitable information sources.
4. User selects one or more sources.
5. AI creates connector definitions.
6. Runtime imports information.
7. AI creates mapping suggestions.
8. User approves.
9. Dashboard updates automatically.
